transcript:
Customer: Hello?
Executive: Hello, hi sir, good evening, mai shubham baat kar raha hu.
Customer: Ha bhai.
Executive: Aapki baat hui aapni team se?
Customer: Team se kaha baat hui wo to tumse baat karne ki keh rahe hai.
Executive: To unko yahi ab maine jo aapko bheja tha document unko boliye na unse dekh ke nahi ho raha hai.
Customer: Nahi ho pa raha na?
Executive: Nahi.
Customer: Wo team se unse nahi ho pa raha hai waha se data.
Customer: Nahi.
Executive: Ji sir.
Executive: Aapko maine ek screenshot bhi bheja tha sir aise aap jaise wo karte ho na wo ho jayega waha pe.
Customer: Check kar raha hu mai aapka kya batao.
Executive: Ho gaya aapka concern sir.
Customer: Inko kya batau matlab.
Customer: Wo team se baat kara do na ek baar.
Executive: Hello.
summary:
Concerns:

- Customer is unable to access data.

- Customer wants executive to talk to team.

- Executive said he sent a screenshot.
